Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't sense the presence of\Nanyone around the Tenchi Bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.53,0:00:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that means there won't\Nbe any Akatsuki ambush, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Then let's proceed\Nas planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:00:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take this and\Nhold it towards me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.59,0:01:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's good.\NHold it towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wood Style: Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Did it turn out okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it did!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like Sasori's puppet\NHiruko in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I want to adjust the voice.\NLet me know when it sounds right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!\NThat's it. That's the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we're going to start\Nthe operation, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tone is too polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to sound more violent\Nor surly or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm irritable, and hate waiting\Nand being kept waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're starting the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right-right.\NThat's what he was like!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, our opponent should be\Non the alert. We'll split up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Observe teamwork at all times!\NEspecially you, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be jumping out before\NI give the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay...Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wind's strong. This should...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, this spot should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's almost noon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That spy jerk...isn't he here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:12.11,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(747,615)}The Tenchi Bridge\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At midday in ten days,\N{\i1}go to the Tenchi Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}located in\N{\i1}the Village Hidden in the Grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got a spy working as one\N{\i1}of Orochimaru's subordinates...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was supposed to\N{\i1}rendezvous...with him...there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's him, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Captain Yamato...\N{\i1}I hope you do okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Lord Sasori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been five years, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kabuto Yakushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you followed...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've still got the strange sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,from when I remembered who I was\Nafter your Jutsu broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I still feel heavy-headed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Him again...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought...\Nthe Akatsuki spy was Kabuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much time,\Nso please keep it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I risked my life to get here\Nwithout Orochimaru finding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want information about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the location of his hideout\Nand Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There are several hideouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We move to\Na different hideout each week
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so as not to get discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course there are hideouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,not just in the Village Hidden\Nin the Sound, but in other lands as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Spies for Orochimaru infiltrate\Nand act as informers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are all sorts of\Nmeans of transport,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so they're not easily tracked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're now in a hideout
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,on a small island on\Na lake to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be moving again in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke Uchiha is there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the wind is so loud\NI can't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! That's why we were\Nable to get this close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind blows away the noise and\Nsmell, so we can sit here unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...it's just a wild rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,About what you ordered me to do,\NLord Sasori...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still had a few more things\N{\i1}I wanted to ask him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}while I had the chance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be discovered if the conversation\N{\i1}continues any further...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after his reincarnation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru uses a Jutsu\Nto apply a protector
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to the cellular specimens\Nfrom his discarded body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore I was unable\Nto analyze the cellular data.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?!\NHe should just grab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,His opponent is Kabuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Being overly cautious is just fine.\NIt's all over if he gets away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The spy could get suspicious\Nif he's too cautious...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the timing to capture him\Nwill get thrown off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,just have to believe in\NCaptain Yamato about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please hand over\Nthe item in question immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be hanging around here\Nany longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's discovered that I'm here\Nwith you like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't hold out any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just have to capture him\N{\i1}here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That conversation sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you guys let me\Njoin in as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was followed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't pulled out\Na Kunai Knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have been able\Nto get away before I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks like he's\N{\i1}misunderstood nicely...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I still haven't been\N{\i1}discovered for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...now that Orochimaru\N{\i1}has shown up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That outfit...sure takes me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasori...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you follow Kabuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I just thought I'd thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This kid you sent to me...\Nhas come in very handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of human subjects\Nnecessary for the development
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of one new Jutsu is over a hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to this kid's Medical Ninjutsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been able to reuse\Ntest subjects several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a great shortage\Nof them, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to stand by until\Nthe Captain gives us instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would probably be\N{\i1}impossible for me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} to take on Orochimaru alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even if I can stop Orochimaru\N{\i1}by working together with Kabuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he'll find out immediately that\N{\i1}I'm not Sasori by my fighting style...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so, if I call those three...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then Kabuto will find out\N{\i1}who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and it will become difficult\N{\i1}to capture him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Either I have to immediately call\N{\i1}the three and defeat both of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or retreat as is without calling them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to do one or the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have I been discovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple Striking Shadow Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Substitution created\Nwith the Wood Style Ninjutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You... could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochimaru.\NIs this Sasori's real body?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabuto... you didn't know\Nhis real face
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,even though you were\Nhis subordinate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a broody guy\Nwho always stayed hidden
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,inside his puppets, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabuto... you were supposed\Nto be an Akatsuki spy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you caught in one\Nof Sasori's Jutsu all this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochimaru...broke that Jutsu\Nfor me ages ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you went\Nto the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending to be caught\Nin one of Sasori's Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get caught in one\Nof Orochimaru's Jutsu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No... that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just empathize with\NLord Orochimaru's ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan was to take\Ncare of Sasori.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But something has gone\Nquite wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabuto... I'll tell you\Nabout this kid later...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you call the three\Nlittle mice behind you over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he's seen through\N{\i1}everything, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You again, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen that face often...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looks like\Nthe Nine-Tails kid's here, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll play with you guys a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see who's gotten stronger,\Nyou...or Sasuke.
